    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it is a total dream! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is in flawless, like-new condition\u2014truly a rare find. It drives like it just rolled off the lot, and the interior is still smelling fresh. If you\u2019re looking for a gem that\u2019s been loved and pampered, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
