    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless E46 M3, a definitive driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, having undergone proactive VANOS bulletproofing and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, while the M-Variable Differential provides optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity, delivering the precise lateral dynamics expected of a flagship M-car. With original paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key specimen for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
