      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the leather remains supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and that signature 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the navigation interface, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it has been maintained exclusively by certified technicians with a full binder of service records to prove it. This isn't just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
