    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I've babied this thing since day one, keeping it spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that new-car magic. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
