    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, an analog masterpiece featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. This example is mechanically flawless, having undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe carrier. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, positive engagement, paired with the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and an unmolested suspension geometry. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is commensurate with its mechanical excellence\u2014zero stone chips, original VIN tags on all panels, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
